title: 'Affordable luggage trolley'
body: Have been using the suitcase for last couple of months and I travel almost every other week for business/work. It is affordable and rugged. It's okay for 3-4 pair of clothes and small items like shaving kit, a pair of flip flops etc. The body is scratch prone but the patterns actually help in covering a lot of light scratches. The design and color is helpful in locating the bag on luggage carousel in an airport amidst a crowd of black and grey luggage cases. One star less for the stability of the trolley while standing
